# Phase 2.9: Remaining Controllers

## Goal

Implement the 5 remaining protected controllers to complete the API.

---

## Controllers to Create

### 1. AddressController
- [index()](file:///home/project/atelier-arome/atelier-arome-api/app/Http/Controllers/Api/V1/TagController.php#13-33) — List user addresses
- `store()` — Create new address
- [update()](file:///home/project/atelier-arome/atelier-arome-api/app/Http/Controllers/Api/V1/CartController.php#80-109) — Update address
- `destroy()` — Delete address

### 2. OrderController
- [index()](file:///home/project/atelier-arome/atelier-arome-api/app/Http/Controllers/Api/V1/TagController.php#13-33) — List user orders with pagination
- [show()](file:///home/project/atelier-arome/atelier-arome-api/app/Http/Controllers/Api/V1/CategoryController.php#31-58) — Get single order by order number

### 3. WishlistController
- [show()](file:///home/project/atelier-arome/atelier-arome-api/app/Http/Controllers/Api/V1/CategoryController.php#31-58) — Get user wishlist with items
- [addItem()](file:///home/project/atelier-arome/atelier-arome-api/app/Http/Controllers/Api/V1/CartController.php#32-79) — Add product to wishlist
- [removeItem()](file:///home/project/atelier-arome/atelier-arome-api/app/Http/Controllers/Api/V1/CartController.php#110-129) — Remove product from wishlist

### 4. ReviewController
- `store()` — Create review (verified purchase check)
- [update()](file:///home/project/atelier-arome/atelier-arome-api/app/Http/Controllers/Api/V1/CartController.php#80-109) — Update own review
- `destroy()` — Delete own review

### 5. CheckoutController
- `initiate()` — Validate cart, create pending order
- `complete()` — Process payment, confirm order

---

## Implementation Order

1. AddressController (simple CRUD)
2. WishlistController (simple add/remove)
3. OrderController (read-only for users)
4. ReviewController (with purchase verification)
5. CheckoutController (complex, needs order creation)

